{"tid":1462201,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"忍唔撚住，真係要屌曬你哋老母!!!!","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:35.000Z","uid":136727,"like":244,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"d13ecd4069fcceccf1bdf2d3b84a4457be68375f","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"幾個post就互帶風向喺度互屌分化又捉鬼捉邪，可唔可以大家有獨立思考呀？<br />\n停三秒諗吓我哋今日入去機場目標係乜?<br />\n諗唔到嘅自修三嘢收隊啦屌!<br />\n有人話要阻人搞旅客吖嘛？<br />\n好，你哋即管做，不過唔撚好拉其他人同你一齊做，唔做屌人係鬼嘅，咁你係咩先?<br />\n各有各做喎，核彈都唔割喎????<br />\n去撚曬邊???<br />\n麻煩做任何事之前，三思 而後行，好無?"},{"pid":"ea9aecbdddfacba8305fa3254f44db721f8e2a62","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afd894dc97b219e93a24bb55d690de75cca95760","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:12:17.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"51bc7612a3504cca2e0e03457799fb98106f1fb2","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:12:28.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1a1d3e3140a7fd325f49f16be5dada3c77093ac8","tid":1462201,"uid":221412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:12:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc5a2c7162679c773d362cecc4df4dde6eea0ac9","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:12:38.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"40b2ff4639a2111bb7f4f5d0ac99e42eccce6bda","tid":1462201,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:12:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebc1205af83459ff12a95bbf33c4688d69ba1e15","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:12:48.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"5e08507f69f902185e11842acea022283d7035d4","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:13:00.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"0d6a8061d03e681bf7ca30eedf9cff0bf54244