d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4373652fd67ea4a649e1781c151645f07dab23","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96aa9c3ebc937ab5fa184a27b539a55c240cf568","tid":1462201,"uid":28831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:19:27.000Z","msg":"從來都冇人屌人唔做<br />\n每次都係d散水撚走出黎屌人做先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2807b36ccdaeaa3ea0ce8f7506da393b50bfa83d","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96aa9c3ebc937ab5fa184a27b539a55c240cf568","tid":1462201,"uid":28831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:19:27.000Z","msg":"從來都冇人屌人唔做<br />\n每次都係d散水撚走出黎屌人做先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:21:02.000Z","msg":"唔好理，各有各做，睇吓到時邊邊人多就夠，別有用心嘅自然會露出尾巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5185bdc4ec1c17e58b9135f7224bda6fa7b2e0e0","tid":1462201,"uid":295218,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"好撚肯定傳停飛果班，唔係狗就係弱智<br />\n<br />\n成個下午都唔停<br />\n偏偏收工時間先嚟停，為乜？<br />\n等你班撚樣見做咗成日嘢，攰攰地，就諗住停飛咗所以返屋企抖，然後無人入去<br />\n<br />\n你老闆，尋日係咁，今日又係咁，醒未呀！<br />\n入機場啦<br />\n轉頭過咗收工時間，復飛又無人岀<br />\n然後旅客又怪落班示威者度<br />\n<br />\n叫大家傳開去<br />\nP牌仔今日開咗post ，無得再開<br />\n一定要入機場"},{"pid":"fe7f478afa2b010c06878b3dcad0cc7e49bc7acc","tid":1462201,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2807b36ccdaeaa3ea0ce8f7506da393b50bfa83d","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96aa9c3ebc937ab5fa184a27b539a55c240cf568","tid":1462201,"uid":28831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":