eplyTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"rite!!!"},{"pid":"f9390b8e8468b50375a9143b8494ed9db6f3ace3","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fa494adcf0d8a133bfa203e74cd85a7c977f71b","tid":1462201,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"真係成功分化左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be5f3c988f3955ac6f1f3e6bb63bffa22bf81a3","tid":1462201,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:24:20.000Z","msg":"發現平民如何令恆指斷崖式大瀉之密技<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1461805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1461805</a>"},{"pid":"5265bd00f3f4d3802eb237942960b04c311cbced","tid":1462201,"uid":254361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:25:13.000Z","msg":"推推推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n行動前，用腦諗下，要自主思考呀<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n同埋連登被滲透之下<br />\n各種謠言滿天飛，更加要冷靜思考<br />\n要多方面去驗證嗰篇文是否真實<br />\n再去諗下佢發呢個信息個目的係乜嘢<br />\n諗下佢背後有沒隱藏的意思（例如分化、恐慌、煽動、造謠等等）<br />\n<br />\n和理非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」「V怪客」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里的大反派說了這麼幾句<br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以用你的力量與聲音，用你的方法去「抗爭」<br />\n力量聲音沒分大細，沒分方法嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（細音說，方法有分成本與效益）<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"77ff556e9d1dc97978ed77f8eb66065c38f3c887","tid":1462201,"uid":201375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:25:52.000Z","msg":"不割蓆分化<br />\n成日話現場係鬼，你估冷氣軍師唔可以係鬼？<br />\n政府back office多人過係機場既前線呀！！<br />\n我淨係知：有人就做乜都贏<br />\n有咩就入機場講，想知判斷既就問在場巴絲<br />\n入曬機場就算你有咩意見我地都可以達到目的"},{"pid":"4cc0b45d02d927ebf6a797183662763589640938","tid":1462201,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:26:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fec1b96980105e1a335f94ff3172d2822779d0de","tid":1462201,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:26:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家係靠緊旅客保護<br />\n你想幾日貨仔就消耗完旅客就去阻啦</span><br />\n<br />\n黑警追殺大家已經由公共空間（街）轉去私人空間（商場，地鐵），暫時未入國際空間（機場）．你玩殘班旅客，按NewYork當年武力驅散和平佔領的文明理據，黑警唔駛諗計都可以入埋機場捉人．到時大家又可以轉去邊？<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n812 係因為真係好多好人，外國旅客只會無奈，唔會不滿．大家做嘅係宣傳，係向國際要求支援，&quot;癱瘓機場&quot;係無可避免嘅副產品．<br />\n今日係一班人搞事．光環變幼稚．當&quot;癱瘓機場&quot;係目標的話，唔係黑警網上帶風，就係衝衝仔唔用腦DNA作怪．"},{"pid":"875877314de7c115e0e8dcef26d2cca628916397","tid":1462201,"uid":237633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"而家變左機場版不合作運動"},{"pid":"a8aa7cf437dc6ef4d89d804acd6fa3897bd5e6ab","tid":1462201,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:27:18.000Z","msg":"你覺得你阻人啲人會覺得政府仆街<br />\n定係<br />\n你地示威者抵撚死，政府快啲清場"},{"pid":"b2851b7654dae3a8842296d61fe501d8712adb4a","tid":1462201,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:27:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bfbbf3b6e27f59251d4002a8b2d67cf6fc78e74","tid":1462201,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62de0fee9b88e9a73d8cd2d724e701ade869d755","tid":1462201,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"3ab4744a1553e04f1ec465d0fadd8affddcbd2fa","tid":1462201,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:29:51.000Z","msg":"幫旅客打比領事館<br />\n比壓力香港政府"},{"pid":"065e71e7378e2e846d569b2987064755674fd278","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:31:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我宣佈，今日水軍大勝!!!!<br />\n今日係連燈仔智商pop quiz fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b20213c4aec724f25895d9f7e2578f04e496540c","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:32:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cde397a2931841cfe363b5c777a5719f3f6bd36e","tid":1462201,"uid":211701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jn0hN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jn0hN8.jpg&h=a1856cc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bd7db16e9dc884099970ec7bd5c2f2e93972721","tid":1462201,"uid":56512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:36:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15f70e2ebc7720a900d3ae8b73e875d17cacc73f","tid":1462201,"uid":279266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9f0829603798cb55c280fb51e27136997209490","tid":1462201,"uid":63870,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:13:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兩邊都唔係鬼，但兩邊都有鬼帶緊風向互屌</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:00.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n所以大家要有獨立思諗有諗個利弊<br />\n同埋雖然前車之鑒，但係都要諗一諗個目的同效能先做<br />\n唔好衝動"},{"pid":"3109168a5f52e9396a79aabd43d529a025dc47af","tid":1462201,"uid":103802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9af7a6b6baa9a65ccd7edfe18ee9eb834a4f813","tid":1462201,"uid":305482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"覺得做法唔好可以檢討！事後先檢討！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7051d6fd06370d9610c06022afa10cb9711193","tid":1462201,"uid":7718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:38:01.000Z","msg":"推 白清有道理"},{"pid":"ab2f6bef594d8102ec528b2bd5e5b267ee570ebc","tid":1462201,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d13ecd4069fcceccf1bdf2d3b84a4457be68375f","tid":1462201,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"幾個post就互帶風向喺度互屌分化又捉鬼捉邪，可唔可以大家有獨立思考呀？<br />\n停三秒諗吓我哋今日入去機場目標係乜?<br />\n諗唔到嘅自修三嘢收隊啦屌!<br />\n有人話要阻人搞旅客吖嘛？<br />\n好，你哋即管做，不過唔撚好拉其他人同你一齊做，唔做屌人係鬼嘅，咁你係咩先?<br />\n各有各做喎，核彈都唔割喎????<br />\n去撚曬邊???<br />\n麻煩做任何事之前，三思 而後行，好無?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:38:06.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好阻離境啦；屌你老尾深圳閪笑尻你地岸尻咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地輿論已經spin哂落黑衣人搞搞震<br />\n<br />\n你幫人地做文宣咋岸尻<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好怪人地割席；係你班友仔冇計劃既後果</span></span>"},{"pid":"c32020bf785376ed6d828976a07280c5889dc3c0","tid":1462201,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ed1a1f33d67a7dd723c465c917cc873104d5a8","tid":1462201,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29fff4998fcada5dbcedd06f3b572ec7316e664","tid":1462201,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:41:58.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong></span><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></span></strong><br />\n但記得大家塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></span></strong><br />\n建議集中火力搵出影響力最大嘅時間<br />\n睇下邊段時間最多人能響應，找出平衡<br />\n用隔日形式塞爆<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以最大化個運動成效</span></span></strong><br />\n隔日嘅好處係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">避免大家過勞和積累</span></strong>過多<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">外國民怨</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地團結一致</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"69a4a0ec8fea9c3683cb7fd5bf8fda441cf4cf8b","tid":1462201,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:47:32.000Z","msg":"兩邊都有鬼帶緊風向<br />\n一邊就引人鬧和理非唔去和理非活動累勇武衝動<br />\n另一邊就引人鬧勇武再騎劫和理非就唔會出嚟<br />\n<br />\n總之無論咩講法都好，用下個腦再自己決定點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d40e04b97b67100b3f4ef2b0dd46d541ac61767","tid":1462201,"uid":57443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:51:37.000Z","msg":"岩，各有各做，唔好屌"}]}